\par \pard\plain \s26\sb120\sa120 \f5\fs20 Besides drawing and painting, the BGI graphics system offers several predicates for manipulating images and pixels.
\par \pard\plain \s16\sa120 \f5\fs20 You can capture a portion of the on-screen image with {\uldb\cf11 getimage}{\i\v getimage_5}, call {\uldb\cf11 imagesize}{\v imagesize_5}
