\par \pard\plain \s16\sa120 \f5\fs20 When you want to link the device drivers and fonts into your .EXE file, you must use the compiler directives {\uldb\cf11 bgidriver }{\v bgidriver_compiler_directive} and {\uldb\cf11 bgifont}{\v bgifont_compiler_directive}
